reviewText: These shows are mostly other cooks. Dave a nd Si make brief appearances and their personalities don't get a chance to shine.

We loved Hairy Bikers videos like "Food Tour of Britain" and so got a PAL DVD player so we could see more.  This isn't Si and Dave, its a TV show that occasionally has them as guests.  Most of the chefs are unknowns, and many have accents unintelligible for the US audience.  And there are no subtitles.  Unwatchable.
